type.description:

Represents the directory structure for a repository. 
For examples see the reference for <a href='type://org.gradle.api.artifacts.repositories.IvyArtifactRepository#layout(String, org.gradle.api.Action)'>org.gradle.api.artifacts.repositories.IvyArtifactRepository#layout(String, org.gradle.api.Action)</a> 

@since 2.3 (feature was already present in Groovy DSL, this type introduced in 2.3)
